gov.noaa.pmel.sgt
Class VectorKey

java.lang.Object
  gov.noaa.pmel.sgt.VectorKey
All Implemented Interfaces:
DataKey, LayerChild, Moveable, Selectable, java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.EventListener
public class VectorKey
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, DataKey, Moveable, java.beans.PropertyChangeListener

VectorKey is used to create a key for the VectorCartesianRenderer. Multiple lines can be included in the key.

Since:
2.1
Version:
$Revision$, $Date$
Author:
Donald Denbo
